title: A college hoops upset for the history books
text:
A college hoops upset for the history books 3:05pm EDT - 01:14 
For the first time ever in college basketball history, a 16-seed team beat a No. 1 ranked team when the University of Maryland-Baltimore County stunned the University of Virginia in one of the biggest upsets on the court.
